headline: Wheels Up CEO talks jetsetter perks from new Signature membership
summary: Private jet company Wheels Up launches its new Signature Membership offering premium services to customers, like guaranteed booking and access to the company's modernized luxury aircraft. Wheels Up CEO George Mattson joins Yahoo Finance senior reporters Pras Subramanian and Allie Canal in studio to discuss the service's latest offerings and its partnership with Delta Air Lines (DAL). Read up on Delta's endorsement of Wheels Up, increasing its stake in the private aviation firm by $282 million in late 2023.
